rimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/getClientRects\"><code>getClientRects()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/insertNode\"><code>insertNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Range/intersectsNode\"><code>intersectsNode()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/isPointInRange\"><code>isPointInRange()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/selectNode\"><code>selectNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/selectNodeContents\"><code>selectNodeContents()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/setEnd\"><code>setEnd()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/setEndAfter\"><code>setEndAfter()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/setEndBefore\"><code>setEndBefore()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><em><code>setStart()</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/setStartAfter\"><code>setStartAfter()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/setStartBefore\"><code>setStartBefore()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/surroundContents\"><code>surroundContents()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/toString\"><code>toString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbstractRange\"><code>AbstractRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><strong><code>Range.setStart()</code></strong> メソッドは<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a>の開始位置を指定します。</p>\n\n<p><code>startNode</code> が <code>Text</code>, <code>Comment</code>, あるいは <code>CDATASection</code> タイプの <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a>&nbsp; であるとき、<code>startOffset</code>は<code>startNode</code>の開始位置からの文字数です。その他の<code>Node</code>タイプの場合、 <code>startOffset</code>は<code>startNode</code>からの子ノード数です。</p>\n\n<p>開始位置を終了位置よりも下（ドキュメントよりも下）に指定すると <code>ERROR_ILLEGAL_VALUE</code> <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/DOMException\"><code>DOMException</code></a> 例外が投げられます。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>range</em>.setStart(<em>startNode</em>, <em>startOffset</em>);\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"Parameters","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"startnode\"><em>startNode</em></dt>\n <dd><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a> を開始する <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></dd>\n <dt id=\"startoffset\"><em>startOffset</em><code>&nbsp;</code></dt>\n <dd><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a>の開始位置を示す<code>startNode</code>オフセット（非負整数）</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Example","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> range <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createRange</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> startNode <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementsByTagName</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"p\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">item</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> startOffset <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nrange<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setStart</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>startNode<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>startOffset<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"Specifications","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-range-setstart\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM<br><small lang=\"ja\">Range.setStart() の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">現行の標準</span></td>\n   <td>No change.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Traversal-Range/ranges.html#Level2-Range-method-setStart\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 2 Traversal and Range Specification<br><small lang=\"ja\">Range.setStart() の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">廃止</span></td>\n   <td>Initial specification.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.Range.setStart","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Range/setStart/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Document_Object_Model\" title=\"/en-US/docs/DOM/DOM_Reference\">The DOM interfaces index</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Example","id":"example"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specification"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Range.setStart() メソッドはRangeの開始位置を指定します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Range.setStart()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Range.setStart()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Range.setStart()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Range.setStart()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source